ygData.messageBody:
I have seen these items posted claiming improved song affects? I had a mino
horn back when it was a bag on your hand, I know they fixed the graphic, but
did they improve the affect of this instrument? And what about a small
brass trumpet? How do I get one of those? I have seen the parts, but
unless I missed something, I have not see an assembled small brass trumpet?

Thanks for the info

Kerouac Dharmabum lvl 25
Rodcet Nife

p.s. low 20's, try the deepwater doggies in lake rathe -- great exp, but no
loot!!! Great means 3 lvls in 2 days, only 2 deaths :)
